---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="ionmx.dev">
  <main class="container w-full md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 mx-auto p-8 mb-48">
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center m-8">
      <img src="./ionmx.jpg" alt="ionmx" class="rounded-full w-20 object-center border-4 drop-shadow-lg border-stone-100"/>
      <h1 class="pl-4 text-3xl text-stone-100 drop-shadow">Jonathan Hernández</h1>
    </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-300 mb-2">About.</h2>
      <div class="text-stone-300 mb-8">
        Hey there ✌️, I'm a self-taught full-stack software developer. 
        I started web development in 2000, since then, I'm always learning new technologies 
        that bring me tools to solve problems in the best way possible.<br><br>
        I'm currently working at <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://cimav.edu.mx">CIMAV</a>, but I'm open to new opportunities
        where my skills can help. Here is <a class="text-pink-600" href="./jh-resume.pdf">my resume</a>.
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-300 mb-2">Skills.</h2>
      <div class="text-stone-300 mb-8">
        <span class="font-bold">Strong:</span> Ruby, Javascript, PHP, HTML, CSS, MySQL, Git, Ruby On Rails, Linux.<br> 
        <span class="font-bold">Knowledgeable:</span> EmberJS, Python, TypeScript, React, Nginx, Redis, GraphQL, NodeJS.<br><br>
        I prefer to learn skills as I need them, so I can focus on finding solutions to problems instead of trying to implement 
        new technologies for the sake of implementing them.
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-300 mb-2">Projects.</h2>
      <div class="text-stone-300 mb-8">
        I love to contribute to open source, also I like to publish my personal projects or stuff that I develop to 
        learn a particular technology, you can explore my <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://github.com/ionmx?tab=repositories">GitHub repos</a>.<br> 
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-300 mb-2">Reach me.</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 text-stone-300">
        <a class="text-pink-600" href="mailto:jonathan.hernandez@gmail.com">EMail</a>
        <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://twitter.com/ion">Twitter</a>
        <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://github.com/ionmx">GitHub</a>
        <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ionmx/">LinkedIn</a>
        <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://www.hackerrank.com/ionmx">HackerRank</a>
        <a class="text-pink-600" href="https://dev.to/ion">Dev.to</a>
      </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
